This service posts an event object for Github events to your IDoneThis Team.


Supported events are currently:
'push', 'issues', 'issue_comment'


Data:
'event' - The github event type, eg. 'push' for commits
'payload' - The data for the event, varies by event type.

More details on Github events: http://developer.github.com/v3/repos/hooks/

Install Notes
------------

Team Name: Your Teams name can be found on your calendar page https://idonethis.com/cal/<team_name>
Token: You'll need to generate an access token which can be done on your team_settings
